switchCamera 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Switch camera to given vehicle / camera. Mode is one of:  "INTERNAL 
": 1st person "GUNNER": optics / sights "EXTERNAL": 3rd person "GROUP 
": group "VIEW": exactly what spectated unit sees (gun optics, binoculars 
, TI and NV, etc.) (VBS2 1.30+ only) 
 
Note: If you switch to a unit in a vehicle, this command uses the correct 
 turret. 
Syntax:  
 unitName switchCamera mode 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
mode: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing